@apiURL = https://fw-teaching.fi/demo/wdbocms/api/v1/products/

### Get all products
GET {{apiURL}}

### Get One Product
GET {{apiURL}}/1002

### Create new product
POST {{apiURL}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jeans",
    "price": 49
}


### Update product info
PATCH {{apiURL}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 29
}

### Delete all products
DELETE {{apiURL}}/1004